name: PixelFem #3 - Tarana Burke
description:
Tarana Burke is a civil rights activist who was the original founder of the ‘Me Too’ movement, which she started in 2006. It later became a global phenomenon that raised awareness about sexual harassment, abuse, and assault in society in 2017 and beyond.

✺This work is part of PixelFems, an evolving project on the Tezos blockchain celebrating iconic women from the past and present✺
